  "title": "QC Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct daily quality checks on calibration tools and inspection activities</li><li>Perform incoming, in-process, and outgoing inspections based on specifications and drawings</li><li>Use digital inspection systems (iPad / Kizeo, ERP, SAP)</li><li>Handle non-conformance reporting</li><li>Coordinate with operations, admin, and logistics teams</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 1 year of experience in warehousing or QC-related role</li><li>Proficient in MS Office</li><li>Detail-oriented and able to work in a fast-paced environment</li></ul><p><strong>Other Information:</strong></p><ul><li>Location: Kranji</li><li>Timing: 8.30am - 5.30pm</li></ul><p>Interested candidates please kindly send CV to 89524450</p><p>Lee Mei Kiew Geraldine<br />CEI Reg: R1331173<br />Link2 Manpower Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 22C1131</p>",
